{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":771,"text":"When we're designing new products,"},{"time":3042,"text":"services or businesses,"},{"time":5056,"text":"the only time you'll know\nif they're any good,"},{"time":7598,"text":"if the designs are good,"},{"time":9320,"text":"is to see how they're used\nin the real world, in context."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14761,"text":"I'm reminded of that every time\nI walk past Highbury Fields"},{"time":18719,"text":"in north London."},{"time":20183,"text":"It's absolutely beautiful."},{"time":21525,"text":"There's a big open green space."},{"time":23246,"text":"There's Georgian buildings\naround the side."},{"time":25838,"text":"But then there's this mud trap\nthat cuts across the middle."},{"time":29720,"text":"People clearly don't want to walk\nall the way around the edge."},{"time":33196,"text":"Instead, they want to take the shortcut,"},{"time":35356,"text":"and that shortcut is self-reinforcing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38866,"text":"Now, this shortcut\nis called a desire path,"},{"time":42186,"text":"and it's often the path\nof least resistance."},{"time":44710,"text":"I find them fascinating,"},{"time":46067,"text":"because they're often the point\nwhere design and user experience diverge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52164,"text":"Now at this point, I should apologize,"},{"time":54041,"text":"because you guys are going to start\nseeing these everywhere."},{"time":56937,"text":"But today, I'm going to pick\nthree I find interesting"},{"time":59623,"text":"and share what actually it reminds me"},{"time":61758,"text":"about launching new products and services."},{"time":65137,"text":"The first is in the capital city\nof Brazil -- Brasilia."},{"time":69203,"text":"And it reminds me that sometimes,"},{"time":71365,"text":"you have to just focus\non designing for a real need"},{"time":74517,"text":"at low friction."},{"time":76251,"text":"Now, Brasilia is fascinating."},{"time":77788,"text":"It was designed by Niemeyer in the '50s."},{"time":80954,"text":"It was the golden age of flying,"},{"time":83186,"text":"so he laid it out like a plane,\nas you can see there."},{"time":86474,"text":"Slightly worryingly,"},{"time":87663,"text":"he put most of the important\ngovernment buildings in the cockpit."},{"time":91435,"text":"But if you zoom in,\nin the very center of Brasilia,"},{"time":93906,"text":"just where the point is there,"},{"time":96092,"text":"you see it's littered with desire paths."},{"time":98973,"text":"They're absolutely everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101070,"text":"Now, they thought that they\nhad future-proofed this design."},{"time":103964,"text":"They thought in the future\nwe wouldn't need to walk anywhere --"},{"time":107003,"text":"we'd be able to drive --"},{"time":108575,"text":"so there was little need\nfor walkways or pavements."},{"time":112358,"text":"But as you can see, there's a real need."},{"time":115564,"text":"These are very dangerous desire paths."},{"time":117410,"text":"If we just pick one, in the middle,"},{"time":119471,"text":"you can see it crosses\n15 lanes of traffic."},{"time":122902,"text":"It won't surprise you guys"},{"time":124682,"text":"that Brasilia has five times\nthe pedestrian accident rate"},{"time":128246,"text":"of your average US city."},{"time":130968,"text":"People are resourceful."},{"time":132479,"text":"They'll always find the low-friction route"},{"time":135537,"text":"to save money, save time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138493,"text":"Not all these desire paths are dangerous,"},{"time":140500,"text":"I was reminded flying here\nwhen I was in Heathrow."},{"time":143917,"text":"Many of us get frustrated\nwhen we're confronted"},{"time":146461,"text":"with the obligatory walk\nthrough duty-free."},{"time":151024,"text":"It was amazing to me"},{"time":152199,"text":"how many people refused to take\nthe long, meandering path to the left,"},{"time":156358,"text":"and just cut through to the right,"},{"time":158459,"text":"cut through the desire path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160813,"text":"The question that's interesting is:"},{"time":162545,"text":"What do designers think\nwhen they see our behavior here?"},{"time":166198,"text":"Do they think we're stupid?"},{"time":168013,"text":"Do they think we're lazy?"},{"time":170405,"text":"Or do they accept\nthat this is the only truth?"},{"time":172981,"text":"This is their product."},{"time":175134,"text":"We're effectively\nco-designing their product."},{"time":178540,"text":"So our job is to design\nfor real needs at low friction,"},{"time":183490,"text":"because if you don't,\nthe customer will, anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187238,"text":"The second desire path I wanted to share"},{"time":189482,"text":"is at the University of California."},{"time":191758,"text":"And it reminds me"},{"time":192934,"text":"that sometimes the best way\nto come up with a great design"},{"time":196116,"text":"is just to launch it."},{"time":198864,"text":"Now, university campuses are fantastic\nfor spotting desire paths."},{"time":202762,"text":"I think it's because students\nare always late and they're pretty smart."},{"time":206124,"text":"So they're dashing to lectures."},{"time":207630,"text":"They'll always find the shortcut."},{"time":210436,"text":"And the designers here knew that."},{"time":212530,"text":"So they built the buildings"},{"time":214527,"text":"and then they waited a few months\nfor the paths to form."},{"time":217830,"text":"They then paved them."},{"time":219378,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":220441,"text":"Incredibly smart approach."},{"time":222719,"text":"In fact, often, just launching\nthe straw man of a service"},{"time":225866,"text":"can teach you what people really want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228667,"text":"For example, Ayr Muir in Boston\nknew he wanted to open a restaurant."},{"time":232885,"text":"But where should it be?"},{"time":234675,"text":"What should the menu be?"},{"time":236661,"text":"He launched a service,"},{"time":238174,"text":"in this case a food truck,"},{"time":239884,"text":"and he changed the location each day."},{"time":242283,"text":"He'd write a different menu\non the side in a whiteboard marker"},{"time":245851,"text":"to figure out what people wanted."},{"time":248218,"text":"He now has a chain of restaurants."},{"time":250661,"text":"So it can be incredibly efficient"},{"time":252716,"text":"to launch something\nto spot the desire paths."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256232,"text":"The third and final desire path\nI wanted to share with you"},{"time":259338,"text":"is the UNIH."},{"time":261594,"text":"It reminds me that the world's in flux,"},{"time":263907,"text":"and we have to respond to those changes."},{"time":266770,"text":"So as you'll guess, this is a hospital."},{"time":269337,"text":"I've marked for you on the left\nthe Oncology Department."},{"time":272735,"text":"The patients would usually stay\nin the hotels down on the bottom right."},{"time":278030,"text":"This was a patient-centered organization,"},{"time":280267,"text":"so they laid on cars for their patients."},{"time":283871,"text":"But what they realized when they started\noffering chemotherapy"},{"time":287287,"text":"is the patients rarely\nwanted to get in cars."},{"time":290088,"text":"They were too nauseous,\nso they'd walk back to their hotels."},{"time":294014,"text":"This desire path that you see\ndiagonally, formed."},{"time":297616,"text":"The patients even called it\n\"The Chemo Trail.\""},{"time":300930,"text":"Now, when the hospital\nsaw this originally,"},{"time":303023,"text":"they tried to lay turf\nback over it, ignore it."},{"time":306744,"text":"But after a while, they realized\nit was an important need"},{"time":309884,"text":"they were meeting for their patients,"},{"time":311685,"text":"so they paved it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313017,"text":"And I think our job is often\nto pave these emerging desire paths."},{"time":316890,"text":"If we look back at the one\nin North London again,"},{"time":320040,"text":"that desire path hasn't always been there."},{"time":322856,"text":"The reason it sprung up"},{"time":324396,"text":"is people were traveling to the mighty\nArsenal Football Club stadium"},{"time":328518,"text":"on game days,"},{"time":329693,"text":"from the Underground station\nyou see on the bottom right."},{"time":332805,"text":"So you see the desire path."},{"time":334128,"text":"If we just wind the clock\nback a few years,"},{"time":336966,"text":"when the stadium was being constructed,"},{"time":339187,"text":"there is no desire path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341797,"text":"So our job is to watch\nfor these desire paths emerging,"},{"time":346567,"text":"and, where appropriate, pave them,"},{"time":348975,"text":"as someone did here."},{"time":351191,"text":"Someone installed a barrier,"},{"time":354076,"text":"people started walking across\nand round the bottom as you see,"},{"time":357320,"text":"and they paved it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358542,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360146,"text":"But I think this is a wonderful\nreminder as well,"},{"time":362558,"text":"that, actually, the world is in flux."},{"time":364434,"text":"It's constantly changing,"},{"time":365680,"text":"because if you look\nat the top of this image,"},{"time":367936,"text":"there's another desire path forming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371413,"text":"So these three desire paths remind me"},{"time":373967,"text":"we need to design for real human needs."},{"time":377579,"text":"I think empathy for what\nyour customers want"},{"time":380086,"text":"is probably the biggest leading indicator\nof business success."},{"time":384315,"text":"Design for real needs"},{"time":386013,"text":"and design them in low friction,"},{"time":389155,"text":"because if you don't offer them\nin low friction,"},{"time":391814,"text":"someone else will, often the customer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394875,"text":"Secondly, often the best way\nto learn what people really want"},{"time":399059,"text":"is to launch your service."},{"time":400947,"text":"The answer is rarely inside the building."},{"time":403751,"text":"Get out there and see\nwhat people really want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406706,"text":"And finally, in part\nbecause of technology,"},{"time":409173,"text":"the world is incredibly flux\nat the moment."},{"time":412010,"text":"It's changing constantly."},{"time":413993,"text":"These desire paths are going\nto spring up faster than ever."},{"time":417730,"text":"Our job is to pick the appropriate ones"},{"time":420701,"text":"and pave over them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422572,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423747,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}